==Conditional Visa on arrival (VoA)==
*Citizens of the following 15 countries and territories can obtain a visa on arrival at [[Beirut International Airport]] or any other port of entry '''only''' if there is no Israeli stamps, visas, or seals on their passport and provided holding, a non-refundable return or circle trip ticket, a copy of a reservation in a 3 to 5 star hotel or private residential address with telephone number in the Republic of [[Lebanon]], and at least '''USD 2,000 in cash'''<ref>[https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_client.cgi?ExpertMode=TIDFT/LB/VI/IS/ID7643&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C]</ref>

